title: Maureen O'Hara passes away at 95
text: Maureen O'Hara passes away at 95 Sunday, 25 October 2015 (7 minutes ago) London, Oct. 25 : Actress Maureen O'Hara has passed away at the age of 95. Maureen O'Hara, the flame-haired Irish movie star who appeared in classics ranging from the grim "How Green Was My Valley" to the uplifting "Miracle on 34th Street", has passed away.
